    &lt;howtoavoid>Follow lockout procedure before servicing.&lt;/howtoavoid>
    <b>&lt;hazardsymbol keyref="hazard-rotatingblade"/></b>
  &lt;/messagepanel>
&lt;/hazardstatement></codeblock>--></example>
